filozofsko sranje in vse to,

01:00:16.776 --> 01:00:20.051
ampak ali bi mi prinesel

01:00:20.086 --> 01:00:24.092
tisto radijsko postajo?

01:00:27.642 --> 01:00:29.217
Hvala.

01:00:44.012 --> 01:00:47.522
Halo? Ne, ne, delo ima.

01:00:56.783 --> 01:00:59.558
Zakaj si stopil na mino?

